Use hgrc within $TESTTMP

  $ cp $HGRCPATH orig.hgrc
  $ HGRCPATH=`pwd`/hgrc
  $ export HGRCPATH
  $ cp orig.hgrc hgrc

Use an alternate var for scribbling on hgrc to keep check-code from
complaining about the important settings we may be overwriting:

  $ HGRC=`pwd`/hgrc
  $ export HGRC

